high_descs: Turn around and take one step, then turn right and walk across the room, then turn right to face the white counter.
Pick up the knife that is next to the coffee cup.
Turn right and take one step then turn left to face the counter.
Put the knife in the coffee cup that is to the left of the sink.
Pick up the coffee cup with the knife in it.
Turn around and take one step, then turn right and walk to the white table, then turn right to face the black table.
Put the coffee cup with the knife on the right side of the black table.
turn around and walk past the fridge a bit, then turn right and walk over to the kitchen counter to the left of the sink
grab a butter knife off of the kitchen counter
turn to back up and then face the kitchen counter again
place the knife inside of the cup on the counter
pick the cup up off of the counter there
turn to back up a bit and then face the black table to the left of the counter
place the cup down on the black table to the left of the counter
anns.task_desc: place a cup with a knife in it down on the kitchen table

high_descs: Turn around and walk past the refrigerator on your right, and turn right, then go across the kitchen to the small counter on the left side of the sink, to your right.
Pick up the knife that is near the edge of the counter.
Move over to your right so that you are directly in front of the coffee cup on the counter.
Place the knife in the coffee cup.
Pick up the coffee cup with the knife inside, from the counter top.
Move over to your left so that you are directly in front of the small black stand, to the left of the counter.
Place the coffee cup with the knife inside, on the right, front corner of the small, black stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a coffee cup containing a knife on the kitchen stand.
